### Key Animations Implemented

1. **Page transitions** — Smooth fade + slide between all routes via `AnimatePresence`
2. **Skeleton loaders** — Shimmer cards during data fetching (Finder + Home)
3. **Staggered card entrance** — Products appear one by one with 60–70ms delays
4. **Product Detail Modal** — Spring-animated scale+fade overlay with backdrop blur, ESC/click-outside to close
5. **Animated filter panel** — Slide-in/out with height animation
6. **Animated compare bar** — Spring slide-up entrance
7. **Button micro-interactions** — Scale on hover/active with spring feel
8. **Accessibility** — `prefers-reduced-motion` disables all animations

### No New Dependencies

`framer-motion` v11.3 was already installed. No new packages added.

